        "creation_date": 1414082554,
        "body": "<p>Assuming <code>lines<\/code> is a <code>Stream&lt;String&gt;<\/code>:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;CDREvent&gt; events =\n    lines\n        .map(s -&gt; s.split(\";\"))\n        .filter(a -&gt; a.length == 32)\n        .map(a -&gt; new CDREvent(a[0], a[1], a[6], a[13]))\n        .collect(Collectors.toList());\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Map each line to a <code>String[]<\/code>, filter out all arrays that are not of length 32, map each <code>String[]<\/code> to a <code>CDREvent<\/code>, and collect them in a new list.<\/p>\n",
